{"tid":1516110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食飯食到我差d反枱","createTime":"2019-08-29T12:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:23:00.000Z","uid":156683,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fe055ab4d8a0885bee37a90a5d7a83d14722e1cc","tid":1516110,"uid":156683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:26:13.000Z","msg":"好耐冇係屋企食飯<br />\n今日難得全家坐埋一齊食飯<br />\n食食下 我啊媽無啦啦講起班後生有收錢<br />\n我就火都黎 開始反駁佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愈講愈激動 我其他屋企人就話講還講 做咩咁嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲話香港嘅事唔好影響屋企人感情<br />\n我啊媽仲加句:<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有膽就去搞林奠啦你地</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我聽完就冇再食 行返入房 終於明白有藍絲屋企人係幾辛苦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">DLLM</div></span><br />\n如果冇班勇武冇班和理非<br />\n香港人行唔到去今日<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"9275be0abc194a4c5e0689264606d63f15c22fbd","tid":1516110,"uid":11436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:28:22.000Z","msg":"辛苦你喇 我都好耐無同屋企人食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d35a1f9b441fdb4b35123550d7ebeef91c929b","tid":1516110,"uid":260749,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:30:21.000Z","msg":"講還講 做咩咁嬲<br />\n呢句野同我老母講既一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2445595609ae7fbb78361321c623c21a13bd3848","tid":1516110,"ui